{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SMTP","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Glossary/SMTP","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary\">용어 사전</a>\n\n  <ol>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/NNTP\">NNTP <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/POP\">POP3 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">프로토콜</a></li>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/State_machine\">상태 기계 <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li>위키백과\n  <ol>\n   <li><a title=\"SMTP\" href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMTP\">SMTP</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>SMTP</strong>(Simple Mail Transfer Protocol)는 새로운 이메일을 전송할 때 사용하는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">프로토콜</a>입니다.</span> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/POP\">POP3 <small>(en-US)</small></a>나 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/NNTP\">NNTP <small>(en-US)</small></a>처럼, SMTP도 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/State_machine\">상태 기계 <small>(en-US)</small></a> 기반 프로토콜입니다.</p>\n\n<p>SMTP는 상대적으로 직관적입니다. 복잡함을 유발하는 주요 원인은 다양한 인증 방법(<a class=\"external\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generic_Security_Services_Application_Program_Interface\" rel=\" noopener\"><abbr title=\"Generic Security Services Application Program Interface\">GSSAPI</abbr></a>, <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRAM-MD5\" rel=\" noopener\"><abbr title=\"challenge-response authentication mechanism\">CRAM-MD5</abbr></a>, <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NTLM\" rel=\" noopener\"><abbr title=\"NT LAN Manager\">NTLM</abbr></a>, MSN, AUTH LOGIN, AUTH PLAIN...) 지원, 오류 응답 처리, 인증 실패(서버에서 어떤 방법을 지원한다고 주장했으나 사실 아닐 때 등) 시 처리 등입니다.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"SMTP(Simple Mail Transfer Protocol)는 새로운 이메일을 전송할 때 사용하는 프로토콜입니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SMTP","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SMTP","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/glossary/smtp","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/glossary/smtp/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary","title":"용어 사전"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary/SMTP","title":"SMTP"}],"pageTitle":"SMTP - 용어 사전 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}